de.bioforscher.singa.features.identifiers

Class ChEBIIdentifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.bioforscher.singa.features.identifiers.model.AbstractIdentifier<ChEBIIdentifier>
      • de.bioforscher.singa.features.identifiers.ChEBIIdentifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifier<ChEBIIdentifier>, Feature<ChEBIIdentifier>

    public class ChEBIIdentifier
extends AbstractIdentifier<ChEBIIdentifier>
    This identifier is used by the ChEBI Database to identify small molecules.

    The identifier consists of a unique number preceded by the "CHEBI:" suffix.

    See Also:
    ChEBI identifier
